articles.description: Syed Suhail was living the life any teenager would envy. The 19-year-old spent lavishly, was well-dressed, kept changing his two-wheelers and told everyone he dealt in used bikes and scooters.

articles.title: B'luru residents invite ‘Yama’ to travel on potholed road
articles.description: Residents of Anjanapura Main Road in south Bengaluru, who staged a protest some months ago by crossing a pothole-ridden road in a coracle, on Saturday invited ‘Lord Yama’ to travel on the same stretch.
